# Netlify _redirects
#
# The three-host architecture routes requests at the SvelteKit hooks layer
# (hooks.server.ts), not via static redirect rules here. Dashboard routes on
# the apex are redirected to app.getorderlocal.com server-side; auth routes
# on the app subdomain are redirected to getorderlocal.com server-side.
#
# Add path-scoped rules here only for cases that must be handled before the
# SvelteKit app runs (e.g. legacy URL aliases, forced HTTPS for a custom
# domain that isn't the primary Netlify domain).
